column16: Yandy Diaz singles on a line drive to center fielder JaCoby Jones.   Francisco Lindor scores.    Brandon Guyer to 3rd.    Jose Ramirez to 2nd.
Jose Ramirez singles on a sharp line drive to right fielder Tyler Collins.   Francisco Lindor to 3rd.    Brandon Guyer to 2nd.
Edwin Encarnacion called out on strikes.
Francisco Lindor doubles (4) on a fly ball to center fielder JaCoby Jones.
